description: The Goddess moves up a weight class to wrestle The Amazon. Isis took control early but it was obvious that near the end the tables were turning. The Amazon ran out of time, but you can see her improvement every minute as the match goes on. This is one of the most competitive matches to date. However, when it is all over Isis makes Hollie suck her pussy, long and good.
title: Isis (1-0) vs. Hollie (0-1)
